- Subhi ‘Uwaydah, (Rev. Dr.)
- Andreas Van Agt, (Dr.)

Institutional authors include AWR Editorial Board, AWR Board of Advisors, Center for the Study of Christianity in Islamic Lands (CSCIL), and EKD Presservice.</ddi:abstract>
